documentary after all.

01:06.686 --> 01:09.422
It's fine! Even if we didn't win
the Japanese Academy Award,

01:09.422 --> 01:12.992
we had many viewers and received
great box office results!

01:12.992 --> 01:14.118
That's true.

01:14.293 --> 01:19.265
The Japanese Academy Award
can go **** itself in the ***.

01:19.265 --> 01:23.929
