piece of **** award anyways.

01:23.929 --> 01:25.700
Yeah... Yeah...

01:25.700 --> 01:27.973
Uh... I understand you're frustrated,

01:27.973 --> 01:29.975
but what you just said
were too obscene.

01:29.975 --> 01:32.078
I don't think anyone understood you
due to all the bleeping.

01:32.078 --> 01:33.779
But that's not important!

01:33.779 --> 01:35.815
